title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Law Enforcement Vehicles
content:
Use your newfound automotive underworld connections to purchase and own highly desirable, off-the-grid Law Enforcement Vehicles.

These will not be easy to acquire though, and will require you to go above and beyond the law before you can obtain them.

Visit Warstock Cache & Carry to check out the Vapid Stanier LE Cruiser, Police Riot, and Unmarked Cruiser.
